column5: What is the name of my dog?
What is attached to his collar? R___ h___
How many dogs arrived at the park all together after Buddy and I arrived? (Example: One)
What color were the dogs? br______, bl_________ and _______ with black spots
What color was the dog wearing the red collar?
What did the dogs want to do when the arrived? R___ and c___
Did Buddy <u>join in</u> or did he <u>sit on the sidelines</u>?
Where did the dogs go once they were done playing in the field? (by the bushes or under the tree?)
What did we give the dogs under the tree? w_________ and _______ts
What did the dogs do after they drank water and ate their treats? _______
What time did we leave the park?
